e Indian Self-Determination and Education Assistance Act, referred to in subsec. (f)(3), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/638"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–638","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-04"},"text":"Jan. 4, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/2203"},"text":"88 Stat. 2203","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 46 (§ 5301 et seq.) of Title 25, Indians. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s5301"},"text":"section 5301 of Title 25","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id0dc04c28-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 2327, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/210/tI/s117"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–210, title I, § 117","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/332/s1/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–332, § 1(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-31"},"text":"Oct. 31, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/3097"},"text":"112 Stat. 3097","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/554/s1/a/1/tIII/s310"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–554, § 1(a)(1) [title III, § 310]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-12-21"},"text":"Dec. 21, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/2763"},"text":"114 Stat. 2763","children":[],"tail":", 2763A–46; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/20/tII/s2701/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–20, title II, § 2701(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2001-07-24"},"text":"July 24, 2001","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/115/181"},"text":"115 Stat. 181","children":[],"tail":", related to tribally controlled postsecondary vocational and technical institutions, prior to the general amendment of this chapter by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/270"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–270","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Another prior section 2327, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/210/tI/s117"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–210, title I, § 117","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/392/tI/s116"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–392, title I, § 116","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-09-25"},"text":"Sept. 25, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/772"},"text":"104 Stat. 772","children":[],"tail":", related to program evaluation and improvement, prior to the general amendment of this chapter by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/332"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–332","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id0dc04c29-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—Subsecs. (a)(2), (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/224/s116/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–224, § 116(1)","children":[],"tail":", (2), substituted “("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/189"},"text":"Public Law 92–189","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/85/646"},"text":"85 Stat. 646","children":[],"tail":")” for “("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s640a"},"text":"25 U.S.C. 640a","children":[],"tail":" et seq.)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (f)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/224/s116/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–224, § 116(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Tribe” for “tribe” in two places."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (h). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/224/s116/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–224, § 116(4)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “"},{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Indian tribe","children":[],"tail":"” for “"},{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"indian tribe","children":[],"tail":"” in heading of original Act which appears in heading as “Indian Tribe” and substituted “terms ‘Indian’ and ‘Indian Tribe’ have the meanings given the terms ‘Indian’ and ‘Indian tribe’, respectively, in” for “terms ‘Indian’ and ‘Indian tribe’ have the meanings given the terms in” in text."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (i). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/224/s116/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–224, § 116(5)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (i) and struck out former subsec. (i) which authorized appropriations as necessary for fiscal years 2007 through 2012."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/315/s941/j/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–315, § 941(j)(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (a) and struck out former subsec. (a). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The Secretary shall, subject to the availability of appropriations, make grants pursuant to this section to tribally controlled postsecondary career and technical institutions that are not receiving Federal support under the Tribally Controlled College or University Assistance Act of 1978 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s1801"},"text":"25 U.S.C. 1801","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) or the Navajo Community College Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s640a"},"text":"25 U.S.C. 640a","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) to provide basic support for the education and training of Indian students.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/315/s941/j/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–315, § 941(j)(2)(B)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (d) and struck out former subsec. (d). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “Any tribally controlled postsecondary career and technical institution that is not receiving Federal support under the Tribally Controlled College or University Assistance Act of 1978 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s1801"},"text":"25 U.S.C. 1801","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) or the Navajo Community College Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s640a"},"text":"25 U.S.C. 640a","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) that desires to receive a grant under this section shall submit an application to the Secretary in such manner and form as the Secretary may require.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (h)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/315/s941/k/2/D/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–315, § 941(k)(2)(D)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “the Tribally Controlled Colleges and Universities Assistance Act of 1978” for “the Tribally Controlled College or University Assistance Act of 1978”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id0dc04c2a-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id0dc04c2b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2018 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/224"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–224","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2019-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 2019","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/224/s4"},"text":"section 4 of Pub. L. 115–224","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s2301"},"text":"section 2301 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
